step_data.thought: The previous action resulted in an error message stating 'This email address is already subscribed.' This indicates that the email address I attempted to use for the newsletter subscription is already in the system. Since I cannot subscribe with the same email, I need to either use a different email address or inform the user that they are already subscribed. I will choose to inform the user about this situation.
step_data.action: stop('You are already subscribed to the newsletter with this email address.')
